So who's your friend?

270
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,540
Come with me...

271
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:17,240
I'll ask you again.

272
00:17:17,240 --> 00:17:20,950
You two're friends
with that Straw Hat Luffy?

273
00:17:20,950 --> 00:17:24,750
I don't know if Helmeppo-san is, but I am!

274
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:27,930
He said that we are friends
even if we're apart.

275
00:17:29,480 --> 00:17:31,490
I suppose you're aware of this,

276
00:17:31,490 --> 00:17:34,630
but we can't keep people
like that in the Navy.

277
00:17:34,630 --> 00:17:38,570
But fortunately,
I'm the only one who knows it.

278
00:17:39,780 --> 00:17:41,190
Do you wanna be a marine?!

279
00:17:42,690 --> 00:17:43,970
Please wait a second!

280
00:17:43,970 --> 00:17:48,310
It's true that I'm Luffy-san's friend,
but Helmeppo-san has nothing to...

281
00:17:48,310 --> 00:17:51,530
We do! That's why we're here!

282
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:53,410
Helmeppo-san!

283
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:57,430
Idiot! He isn't someone
who'd listen to that now.

284
00:17:57,870 --> 00:18:00,300
It's joint responsibility.
Joint responsibility.

285
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:04,870
What about you, Coby?!
Don't you wanna be one?

286
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:06,160
I do!!

287
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:09,830
Then, stop grumbling
and bring it on already!

288
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:30,290
We're not done yet!

289
00:18:30,290 --> 00:18:31,080
Yeah!

290
00:18:33,650 --> 00:18:34,540
No good!

291
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:56,630
We're not done yet!

292
00:18:57,370 --> 00:19:00,490
We're not dead yet!

293
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,930
You wanna die that bad?

294
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:05,940
I've decided to be a marine.

295
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:06,730
Hm?

296
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:10,360
If I die fighting for it, I'll be happy.

297
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,900
No way we'd give it up yet!

298
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:17,080
I'm a man who will become a Navy officer!

299
00:19:19,980 --> 00:19:20,710
Huh?

300
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:29,000
A Navy officer, huh? That's interesting.

301
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:50,950
People here have been calling
me eccentric for quite a while,

302
00:19:51,150 --> 00:19:54,820
and especially this time,
they said all sorts of things.

303
00:19:55,760 --> 00:20:00,110
Since I brought you here, I have to
train you so that you'll be very useful.

304
00:20:00,650 --> 00:20:03,610
I tested you two to see
what you are really like.

305
00:20:03,950 --> 00:20:05,810
What we're really like?

306
00:20:05,810 --> 00:20:10,650
Although it may appear that you've been
trying hard strengthening your bodies,

307
00:20:10,650 --> 00:20:13,610
I thought you might
still be weak mentally.

308
00:20:13,930 --> 00:20:17,540
So I tested you to see if you're
working with firm determination.

309
00:20:18,050 --> 00:20:20,770
So what's the verdict?

310
00:20:20,770 --> 00:20:22,840
I'll acknowledge your determination.

311
00:20:23,330 --> 00:20:24,100
But...

312
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,970
...you've still got a long way to go!

313
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:33,560
When it comes to weakness,
you guys take the cake!

314
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:36,690
You'll have an intense
special training every day.

315
00:20:36,990 --> 00:20:38,100
Be prepared!

316
00:20:42,100 --> 00:20:44,550
I'll overlook your friend situation.

317
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,670
But don't tell anyone.

318
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:49,820
Just cherish that feeling.

319
00:20:55,380 --> 00:20:59,310
Yes sir! Thank you very much,
Vice-Admiral Garp!!

320
00:21:58,780 --> 00:22:01,020
Alright! Let's go!!

321
00:22:01,290 --> 00:22:03,400
Little Garden...

322
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:05,370
Yeah!

