00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:13,500
I'll hold you in my arms forever

334
00:23:15,140 --> 00:23:18,910
You've got me!

335
00:23:25,310 --> 00:23:27,380
So this is Little Garden!

336
00:23:27,380 --> 00:23:28,980
What's "little" about it?!

337
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:31,650
It's like an undiscovered land.
